AITEX is involved in several international R&amp;D networks, platforms, etc.: TEXTRANET(Textile Transfer Network),GEDRT, CIRFS, European  Technological Textile Platform for the future of Textile-Clothing sector, European Platform for Sport Innovation (EPSI), Bio-based Consortium (BIC),EUMAT(European Technology Platform for Advanced Engineering Materials and Technologies), Captechs of the European Defence Agency (EDA), AISBL A. SPIRE (European Association Sustainable Process Industry through Resource and Energy Efficiency) and ACTE (European Textile Collectivities Association).&#xd;
&#xd;
AITEX places special emphasis on collaboration with the REDIT and FEDIT technology centres, as well as a wide variety of universities and research and technology centres nationally and internationally.&#xd;
AITEX is also part of international certifications networks including TEXTRANET, ÖKO-TEX, GEDRT, GOLF and AELAF.
